      "description": "README.md is the best entry point for understanding Tack Timetable: an AI-powered school schedule generator that combines a Next.js web UI, a Next.js API layer, and a Python CP-SAT constraint solver. It documents both UI variants (the active App Router app and the legacy Vite playground), maps out the full end-to-end generation flow with exact file references, and provides local verification instructions. Reading it first gives you the vocabulary and mental map you will need for every step that follows.",
